sections.comments: VISA 250 001 will be delivered with some online and some in-person components at the UBC Vancouver campus (adhering to physical distancing and health requirements). If registration for this class is blocked, then it is full and you should register on the corresponding waitlist. Students will be periodically moved from the waitlist into the class as seats become available, and notified of their registration via email.

description: Visual print culture, and contemporary and historical technical print practices. Emphasis on hand-drawn intaglio, relief, screen and/or stencil printing, and graphic digital applications.
